DR. CHAKRADHAR PASWAN V. STATE OF BIHAR & ORS [1988] INSC 68; AIR 1988 SC 959; 1988 (3) SCR 130; 1988 (2) SCC 214; 1988 (1) JT 496; 1988 (1) SCALE 459 (8 March 1988)

